fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Fiction</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/science-fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Science Fiction</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/dystopia" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Dystopia</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/classics" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Classics</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/school" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">School</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/literature" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Literature</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/novels" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Novels</span></a></span></span><span tabindex="-1"></span> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small" aria-label="Show all items in the list"><span class="Button__labelItem">...more</span></button></div></ul></div><div class="BookDetails"><div class="CollapsableList"><span tabindex="-1"><span class="Text Text__body3"><div class="FeaturedDetails"><p data-testid="pagesFormat">194 pages, Kindle Edition</p><p data-testid="publicationInfo">First published October 19, 1953</p></div></span></span><span tabindex="-1"></span> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Butto